interactionClaim: Acupressure is well-tolerated when applied appropriately. No adverse events have been reported in clinical studies.
reference: Hsieh LL, Kuo CH, Lee LH, et al. Treatment of low back pain by acupressure and physical therapy: randomised controlled trial. BMJ 2006;332:696-700., Molassiotis A, Sylt P, Diggins H. The management of cancer-related fatigue after chemotherapy with acupuncture and acupressure: a randomised controlled trial. Complement Ther Med 2007;15:228-37.
